      "text": "And the two officers who walked-- and I am with him-- no cut the hand, nothing, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there, in Lublin, no cars.",
